{
  "id": "68ba63221d095beb185fce84",
  "title": "コンパクトな台を持つ滑らかな関数の存在証明",
  "created": 1757045539,
  "updated": 1757045539,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "68ba63221d095beb185fce84",
      "text": "コンパクトな台を持つ滑らかな関数の存在証明",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1757045539,
      "updated": 1757045539
    },
    {
      "id": "68ba632200000000003ad494",
      "text": "from [超函数]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1757045539,
      "updated": 1757045539
    },
    {
      "id": "68ba632300000000003ad495",
      "text": " コンパクトな台を持つ滑らかな関数の存在証明",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1757045539,
      "updated": 1757045539
    },
    {
      "id": "68ba632300000000003ad496",
      "text": "[$ \\phi_1(x)=\\left\\{\\begin{matrix}\\exp\\left({-\\frac{1}{1-x^2}}\\right)\\quad(|x|<1)\\\\0\\quad(|x|\\ge1)\\end{matrix}\\right.]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1757045539,
      "updated": 1757045539
    },
    {
      "id": "68ba632300000000003ad497",
      "text": "\t連続性を示そう。[$ x^2=|x|^2]なので、",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1757045539,
      "updated": 1757045539
    },
    {
      "id": "68ba632300000000003ad498",
      "text": "\t\t[$ \\lim_{\\delta\\to+0}\\exp\\left(-\\frac1{1-(1-\\delta)^2}\\right)=\\lim_{\\delta\\to+0}\\exp\\left(\\frac{-1}{2\\delta-\\delta^2}\\right)=0]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1757045539,
      "updated": 1757045539
    },
    {
      "id": "68ba632300000000003ad499",
      "text": "\t\tこれで[$ |x|\\ge1]の場合と接続された。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1757045539,
      "updated": 1757045539
    },
    {
      "id": "68ba632300000000003ad49a",
      "text": "\t微分可能性を示そう。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1757045539,
      "updated": 1757045539
    },
    {
      "id": "68ba632300000000003ad49b",
      "text": "\t\t[$ \\phi_1'(x)=0'=0\\qquad(|x|>1+0)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1757045539,
      "updated": 1757045539
    },
    {
      "id": "68ba632300000000003ad49c",
      "text": "\t\t[$ \\phi_1'(x)=-\\frac{2x}{(1-x^2)^2}\\exp\\left(-\\frac1{1-x^2}\\right)\\qquad(|x|<1-0)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1757045539,
      "updated": 1757045539
    },
    {
      "id": "68ba632300000000003ad49d",
      "text": "\t\t\t[$ =-\\frac{2x}{(1-x^2)^2}\\phi(x)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1757045539,
      "updated": 1757045539
    },
    {
      "id": "68ba632300000000003ad49e",
      "text": "\t\t\t[$ p_1(x)\\phi(x)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1757045539,
      "updated": 1757045539
    },
    {
      "id": "68ba632300000000003ad49f",
      "text": "\t\t[$ \\lim_{x\\to1-0}\\phi'_1(x)=0]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1757045539,
      "updated": 1757045539
    },
    {
      "id": "68ba632300000000003ad4a0",
      "text": "\t\t\t[$ \\phi(x)]は指数関数なので、左の有理関数よりも速く収束する。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1757045539,
      "updated": 1757045539
    },
    {
      "id": "68ba632300000000003ad4a1",
      "text": "\t\tこれで[$ |x|=1]の場合に接続された。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1757045539,
      "updated": 1757045539
    },
    {
      "id": "68ba632300000000003ad4a2",
      "text": "\t[$ C^\\infty]級であることを示そう。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1757045539,
      "updated": 1757045539
    },
    {
      "id": "68ba632300000000003ad4a3",
      "text": "\t\t有理関数[$ p_k(x)]を利用して、[$ \\phi_1^{(k)}(x)=p_k(x)\\phi_1(x)]とかけると仮定すると、",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1757045539,
      "updated": 1757045539
    },
    {
      "id": "68ba632300000000003ad4a4",
      "text": "\t\t[$ \\phi_1^{(k+1)}(x)=p_k'(x)\\phi(x)+p_k(x)p_1(x)\\phi_1(x)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1757045539,
      "updated": 1757045539
    },
    {
      "id": "68ba632300000000003ad4a5",
      "text": "\t\t\t[$ =\\left\\{p_k'(x)+p_k(x)p_1(x)\\right\\}\\phi_1(x)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1757045539,
      "updated": 1757045539
    },
    {
      "id": "68ba632300000000003ad4a6",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t有理関数[$ p_k(x)]と有理関数[$ p_1(x)]の積[$ p_k(x)p_1(x)]は有理関数",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1757045539,
      "updated": 1757045539
    },
    {
      "id": "68ba632300000000003ad4a7",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t[$ p_k]が有理関数→[$ p_k']も有理関数",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1757045539,
      "updated": 1757045539
    },
    {
      "id": "68ba632300000000003ad4a8",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t有理関数[$ p_k'(x)]と有理関数[$ p_k(x)p_1(x)]の和[$ p_k'(x)+p_k(x)p_1(x)]は有理関数",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1757045539,
      "updated": 1757045539
    },
    {
      "id": "68ba632300000000003ad4a9",
      "text": "\t\t\t[$ =p_{k+1}\\phi_1(x)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1757045539,
      "updated": 1757045539
    },
    {
      "id": "68ba632300000000003ad4aa",
      "text": "\t\tしたがって[$ |x|\\to1-0]の場合に[$ \\phi(x)]の方が速く収束するので、",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1757045539,
      "updated": 1757045539
    },
    {
      "id": "68ba632300000000003ad4ab",
      "text": "\t\t\t[$ \\lim_{|x|\\to1-0}\\phi_1^{(k+1)}(x)=0]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1757045539,
      "updated": 1757045539
    },
    {
      "id": "68ba632300000000003ad4ac",
      "text": "\t\tよって、[$ |x|\\to1+0]の場合と接続される。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1757045539,
      "updated": 1757045539
    },
    {
      "id": "68ba632300000000003ad4ad",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1757045539,
      "updated": 1757045539
    }
  ]
}